# Portfolio — Project Context

Personal portfolio for **Frederick Aurelio Halim** — bilingual EN/中文 site + RAG chat widget.

## Stack
Next.js 16 · React 19 · TypeScript · Tailwind 4 · GSAP · TanStack Query · OpenRouter · Redis/Upstash

## Key files
- `src/utils/data.ts` — static UI copy + chat widget strings (`hero`, `about`, `experience`, `projects`, `stacks`, `details`, `chat`)
- `docs/*.md` — chat knowledge (→ `src/lib/knowledge/index.json` via `npm run index-knowledge`)
- `src/lib/chat/rag-chat-stream.ts` — RAG SSE pipeline
- `src/lib/knowledge/` — navigator, retrieval, suggestions, prompts
- `src/components/chat/ChatWidget.tsx` — chat UI entry (mounted in Providers)
- `src/middleware.ts` — chat session cookie
- `public/` — images, fonts, screenshots

## Workflow
1. User describes the change
2. Facts first — never invent metrics or job history
3. Static copy → `data.ts`; chat facts → `docs/` then re-index; chat logic → `src/lib/chat/` or `src/lib/knowledge/`
4. Minimal diffs; do not commit unless user asks

## Content rules
- Show what you built and why — not adjective bios
- EN and 中文 must match facts
- No AI-slop: leverage, seamless, robust, cutting-edge, passionate, Furthermore

## Docs
- `AGENTS.md` — full agent guide (architecture, env vars, chat pipeline)
